snippet.title: Octopath Traveler II | Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
See what critics are saying about OCTOPATH TRAVELER II - now available on Nintendo Switch™, PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4 and PC via STEAM®.

Will you strike out on a journey to recruit companions, face formidable foes in the dungeon depths, or simply enjoy the beauty of the world?
Every road is yours to take.

Embark on an adventure all your own.
#octopathtraveler2 

https://www.octopathtraveler2.com/
